flowchart TD
  A[User clicks Load Data\nApp.tsx::handleLoad] -->|setLoadState('loading')\nsetLoadMessage(...)| B[StatusBanner load region\nStatusBanner.tsx]
  C[User submits query\nApp.tsx::handleRun] -->|setRunState('loading')\nsetRunMessage(...)| D[StatusBanner run region\nStatusBanner.tsx]
  B -->|state === 'loading'| E[data-processing='true'\nchip text PROCESSING]
  D -->|state === 'loading'| E
  E -->|CSS class status-chip-loading\nstyles.css::@keyframes statusPulse| F[Visible in-flight pulse feedback]
  A -->|loadInternalData resolves| G[setLoadState('success'|'error')]
  C -->|streamAgentRun resolves| H[setRunState('success'|'error')]
  G -->|re-render StatusBanner| I[data-processing='false'\nstatic SUCCESS/ERROR chip]
  H -->|re-render StatusBanner| I

  N1[Decision: expose data-processing attribute\nWhy: deterministic testable state and stable selector]:::note
  N2[Tradeoff: pulse animation is subtle\nWhy: preserve readability and keep reduced-motion safe]:::note
  N1 -.-> B
  N2 -.-> F

  classDef note fill:#121a2c,stroke:#7aa2d6,color:#dce8ff,stroke-dasharray: 4 4;
